{"tid":1957962,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"<手足顯靈> 確 診 警 長 曾 參 與 3月31日 旺 角 鎮 壓","createTime":"2020-04-04T09:40:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T10:39:09.000Z","uid":227801,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1abee6f865ba2f7548cecca72e64662eefd8ef2f","tid":1957962,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T09:40:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518885-20200404.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518885-20200404.htm&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQyre6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=134d5131\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518885-20200404.htm&h=79330218\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518885-20200404.htm</a><br />\n一名駐守西九龍總區的46歲男警長確診新型肺炎。警方回覆本台查詢時表示，該名警長隸屬機動部隊，過去14日曾參與反罪惡巡邏及人群管理行動，包括3月31日晚上曾參與旺角警署附近的<del>人群管理行動</del>鎮壓，參與行動的警務人員均需佩戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n警方說，該名警員前日感到不適，到政府醫院求醫，他沒有外遊記錄，亦非早前確診警員的緊密接觸者。在等候衞生署進一步評估及建議前，與該警長駐守同一隊伍的所有警務人員，將會安排「在家工作」。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，已即時徹底清潔及消毒相關警署設施及警察宿舍並調派人手，確保相關緊急服務不受影響。所有在西九龍機動部隊行動基地工作的警務人員均需佩戴口罩，進出警署人士均需量度體溫。<br />\n<br />\n警方說，會繼續與衞生署保持緊密聯繫，主動提供該名警長近日工作記錄和執勤表等資料，以及安排相關密切接觸者進入檢疫中心接受檢疫。"},{"pid":"cbff49768850c628df2d8421b9a5258171c71eed","tid":1957962,"uid":3302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T09:40:54.000Z","msg":"傻啦 一定係因為有人背後做緊野"},{"pid":"8617085d057d06d474e99d21cdcbf1f3fc6d8eb4","tid":1957962,"uid":58630,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T09:41:11.000Z","msg":"在家工作係咪即係係屋企打老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb03c1ed62032f2e4c55ea090bce414f8064a2ec","tid":1957962,"uid":89184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8617085d057d06d474e99d21cdcbf1f3fc6d8eb4","tid":1957962,"uid":58630,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T09:41:11.000Z","msg":"在家工作係咪即係係屋企打老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T09:42:31.000Z","msg":"真係呀，黑警家暴不能忽視"},{"pid":"8e140054347fbb4fa915039246716c6ea1c2c382","tid":1957962,"uid":65178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb03c1ed62032f2e4c55ea090bce414f8064a2ec","tid":1957962,"uid":89184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8617085d057d06d474e99d21cdcbf1f3fc6d8eb4","tid":1957962,"uid":58630,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T09:41:11.000Z","msg":"在家工作係咪即係係屋企打老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T09:42:31.000Z","msg":"真係呀，黑警家暴不能忽視"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T09:43:03.000Z","msg":"無錯 狗宿大把"},{"pid":"a031403f61e4e1a1cfa6dc209047dc1a4fc28202","tid":1957962,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T09:48:45.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />在天之靈"},{"pid":"a7e518baefd96299461cc8cd2215a0db6b0210e0","tid":1957962,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T09:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0edafef61e86dbb02ef78ec1dcfb65ecfd1f9df5","tid":1957962,"uid":318070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T09:58:17.000Z","msg":"多行不義必自斃"},{"pid":"17b4fb77ddcb41054e40095d296b8a5053f73888","tid":1957962,"uid":192052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb03c1ed62032f2e4c55ea090bce414f8064a2ec","tid":1957962,"uid":89184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8617085d057d06d474e99d21cdcbf1f3fc6d8eb4","tid":1957962,"uid":58630,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T09:41:11.000Z","msg":"在家工作係咪即係係屋企打老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T09:42:31.000Z","msg":"真係呀，黑警家暴不能忽視"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-